{
  "message": "test(fft): raise metamorphic coverage on thin 2D/ND/symmetry relations\n\nAdded 12 goldens for previously single-fixture FFT metamorphic\nrelations:\n\n- fft2_ifft2_inverse: 4x4 square and 2x8 rectangular (existing: 3x3)\n- fftn_ifftn_inverse: 3x4 and 2x2x4 (existing: 2x2x2 only)\n- rfft_hermitian_symmetry: len8 and len16 oscillating (existing: 1 case)\n- fft_scale_reciprocal: negative scale factor and large scale\n  (existing: 1 case)\n- fft_real_dc_component: len4 symmetric and len16 mixed DC\n- fft_conjugate_symmetry: len16 oscillating and len4 asymmetric\n\n30 fft_metamorphic cases total (from 18). Exercises each relation's\nnumerical tolerance across multiple array shapes and sign patterns.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
